In an exclusive interview with ZimTrade, the national trade development and promotion organisation and facilitator of the Zimbabwe country pavilion exhibiting at DRC Mining Week in Lubumbashi from 19 - 21 June reveals that “the reported US$3 million deals done on site last year is an indication that the country is a lucrative market”. This article first appeared in Mining Review Africa Issue 3, 2019 and will be published in full on 16 April 2019 You can read the
